<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulm</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass Niklas Polaner, Bürger zu Nürnberg, eine nicht genannte Geldsumme nicht mehr beansprucht, sodass Klas Halbwachs, Bürger zu Nürnberg, seine Schulden bei Heinrich Seitzler, Bürger zu Ulm, gegen Aushändigung des Schuldbriefs und Quittung bezahlen will.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_11" id="4v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_11_r1l22">Den von Vlme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_11_r1l23"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der ſchuld <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe Clas <expan>halpwachſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l24"><expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> / <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Seıcʒl<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ſchuldıg beleıb . vnd dıe Jm Nıclas Polaner auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l25">vnſer <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> / verheft hab etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l26"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> für vns beſant vnd mıt Jn <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / vnd den <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> Nıclas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l27">Polaner vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geweıſet / daʒ er das verpott <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> das <expan>obg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> gelt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l28">abgetan vnd ledıg geſagt hat / ſo hat der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Clas <expan>halpwachſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l29">wer Jm <expan>ſein<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchuldbrıef antwurt vnd von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> / des ſeıcʒlers <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l30">quittıer . den well er <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> becʒaln / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_line_1588159433095_2279"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Nereȷ et Achılleȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_11" id="4v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Ulme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von der schuld
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex>,</expan> die Clas
                            <expan>Halpwachs<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Seiczl<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, schuldig beleib, und die im Niclas Polaner,
                        auch unser <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, verheft hab etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> für uns besant und mit in
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt und den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> Niclas Polaner umb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> geweiset, daz er das verpott
                                <expan>üb<ex>er</ex></expan> das
                            <expan>obg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> gelt abgetan und ledig gesagt
                        hat. So hat der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Clas
                                <expan>Halpwachs<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, wer im <expan>sein<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        schuldbrief antwurt und von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> des Seiczlers <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        quittier, den well er <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> beczaln. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Nerei et Achillei.</ab>
</div>
